item.title: Intel Finds Great Performance With PostgreSQL's AVX-512 Support
item.description: Back in April PostgreSQL added AVX-512 support for CRC32 computations. That AVX-512 support is found with PostgreSQL 18.0 that released in September and now Intel is praising this addition to PostgreSQL for which their developers also had a part in along with AWS and others...
